                    <h5>What is visDash?</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="row section-content">
                    <p>visDash is an organization and visualization dashboard tool for small scale to large scale organizations and companies. visDash aligns everyone's understanding of the organization's big picture goal, while also facilitating smooth communication between the executives and other employees regarding company priorities and short term goals. </p> 
                    <p>Using visDash encourages transparency and trust within an organization and, if used correctly, ensures that the company or organization's performance drastically increases, leading to increased revenue and/or growth; more importantly, visDash empowers everyone in an organization. </p>
                    
                    <p>The features offered by visDash are: </p>                   
                    <ul>
                        <li>List, communicate, and visualize company's big picture strategic goals</li>
                        <li>List, communicate, and visualize company's smaller picture strategic goals</li>
                        <li>Maps how each specific quarterly, monthly, or weekly strategic goals relate to big picture goals</li>
                        <li>Maps how big picture goals trickle down to specific short term goals</li>
                        <li>Map which goals fall under which department or branch</li>
                        <li>Track the progress of all goals</li>
                        <li>Ownership and accountability of each goal </li>
                        <li>Update any information easily</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p>The teams will determine the quarterly outcomes they want to achieve, visualize the work that theyâ€™re focused on and report on how they are progressing against that work.</p>
